Area Maps

There may be a situation where the data set you want to visualise has geographical location data present too. You can plot geographical data using a very interesting charting type called area maps. In the following lecture, Prof. RC will elaborate more on area maps.

Area maps give you the freedom to add other types of charts on top of itself such as pie charts to create very informative and interactive visualisations. To learn how to create area charts in Tableau, please watch the following lecture:
